ck tether slicing through pale waters and fragmented land masses evokes a quiet, slightly ominous sci-fi atmosphere, but the minimal tonal range limits emotional impact.	{"Deepen contrast around focal points (the docking site and ship) to heighten drama","Introduce subtle color temperature shifts—cool distant blues, warmer foreground grays—to enrich atmosphere","Consider adding small narrative details (lights on the dock, tiny figures, or exhaust plumes) to amplify the sense of scale and story"}	0		{}	2025-02-20	quick sketch
